title: Janet Jackson - Discipline Pre-release
description:
She&#039;s back, and she&#039;s hotter than ever! Witness the birth of a new era in the Janet saga! With the forthcoming release of her new album "Discipline", Janet is exploring new territory and giving it all to you. Included in this torrent is her debut single and radio hit, "Feedback", along with 2 new tracks fresh from the studio, "Rock With U", a sexy dance anthem and "Luv", and urban chart topper just waiting to happen.

So get on board and get ready for Janet in 2008.
